                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5831" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1482</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8375 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“润”物有声：疫情防控常态化下华润医药可持续发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Moisten&quot; things sound : the sustainable development path of China Resources Medicine in the post-epidemic era</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吕荣杰，薛颖，宋婷婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华润医药集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华润医药；战略管理；创新转型；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> China Resources Pharmaceutical; Strategic management; Innovation and transformation; Sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在疫情防控进入常态化阶段、医药行业改革稳步开展的背景下，作为医药行业“巨头”的华润医药却面临着股价下跌、利润下滑及业务板块不均衡等问题，于社会褒贬不一的议论中深陷可持续发展的困境。案例以华润医药效益下降的原因为背景展开，并就如何从“新”开始、多措并举解决问题进而推进可持续发展实现企业价值升级的过程及相关革新策略进行阐述。华润医药针对业务板块不均衡及管理分散等问题采取了哪些战略？华润医药又是如何因地制宜实施的？同时也以华润医药经营战略和公司战略层面的实施情况展现了其发展方向与态势。希望通过对华润医药可持续发展战略案例的讨论与学习，学习者能够深刻掌握企业解决可持续发展困境中实施的战略举措及业务模式等关键要素，加深对企业经营战略与公司战略等理论知识的理解。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of the normalization of epidemic prevention and control and the steady development of the reform of the pharmaceutical industry, China Resources Pharma, as a &quot;giant&quot; in the pharmaceutical industry, is faced with problems such as falling stock prices, declining profits and unbalanced business segments, and is trapped in the dilemma of sustainable development amid mixed social comments. The case is based on the reasons for the decline of the benefits of China Resources Pharmaceutical Co., LTD., and explains how to start from the &quot;new&quot;, take multiple measures to solve the problem and then promote sustainable development to achieve the upgrading of enterprise value and related innovation strategies. What strategies does CRP take to solve the problems of unbalanced business segment and decentralized management? How does China Resources Medicine adapt measures to local conditions? At the same time, the implementation of China Resources Pharmaceutical business strategy and corporate strategy shows its development direction and trend. It is hoped that through the discussion and study of the case of sustainable development strategy of China Resources Pharmaceutical, learners can deeply grasp the key elements such as strategic measures and business models implemented by enterprises to solve the dilemma of sustainable development, and deepen their understanding of the theoretical knowledge of business strategy and corporate strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多元化战略、 一体化战略、 创新战略及企业可持续发展战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-01</td>
                            </tr>
